{
  "stem": "21308.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was congratulating myself on my good luck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, I saw my colonel, who stood about 6 foot 3, and he bellowed across the square, Ted!",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I did what we always did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Orders!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Of course, that meant I had to run.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You always doubled for orders, and you never questioned them when you got them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You had questions at the end, and it was wise to keep the questions to the minimum.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, he told me that they'd heard that there was a pretty awful chaos in a camp near the docks, and that there's a lot of concentration camp people there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that I had to get in there-- he said, actually said to me, I've volunteered to take over cleaning up this mess.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I said, oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, no, you take your unit in, and you clean it up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now that's actually how I went in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And because I only had my own jeep there then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You see, the guns would be way behind, and the men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so I hurriedly gave my orders group a rendezvous, and then I drove in my jeep to this shambles of a mess near the docks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I went down this road, and I just don't know how I got there now, but I remember the first thing I saw were two hospital trains, Wehrmacht hospital trains.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I realized that they were not in this camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were clear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They're on the railway, so that's not my headache.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I drove on, and of course, there's Germans all over the bloody place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Some armed, some not armed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I got into this camp, and I have never seen anything like it in my life.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
